OL,5,G1700 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FDog handler Martyn finds himself
OL,7,     Fin the firing line when he cops a
OL,8,     Ftasty right hook and Dan is given
OL,9,     Fthe runaround by an uninsured
OL,10,     Fdriver.
OL,11,G1800 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FDocumentary series. The
OL,13,     Finterceptors of Durham and
OL,14,     FCleveland tackle a stand-off
OL,15,     Fbetween armed officers and a
OL,16,     Fdangerous knifeman and a man
OL,17,     Fwielding a length of guttering.
