OL,9,G2100 The Surgeon
OL,10,     FBehind the surgeon's mask - from
OL,11,     Fthe pressurised operating theatre
OL,12,     Fto life at home - as consultant
OL,13,     Fheart surgeon Inder Birdi faces
OL,14,     Fone of the most challenging cases
OL,15,     Fof his career.
