OL,5,G0100 #Text Me When You Get Home
OL,6,     FHannah Anderson's best friend
OL,7,     Frealises something is wrong when
OL,8,     FHannah stops responding to her
OL,9,     Ftexts, but no one knows that
OL,10,     FHannah has been abducted by
OL,11,     Fsomeone close to her.
OL,12,G0155 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,14,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,15,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,16,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic,
OL,17,     Fbut that can hugely affect the
OL,18,     Fsufferers.
